quran[27{c,v,t}:
37,127,"magar unhon ne usay jhutla diya, so ab yaqeenan woh saza ke liye paish kiye jaane walay hain"
37,128,bajuz unn bandgaan khuda ke jin ko khalis kar liya gaya tha
37,129,aur ilyas ka zikar kher hum ne baad ki naslon mein baqi rakha
37,130,salam hai ilyas par
37,131,hum neki karne walon ko aisi hi jaza dete hain
37,132,waqai woh hamaray momin bundon mein se tha
37,133,aur loot bhi unhi logon mein se tha jo rasool bana kar beje gay hain
37,134,yaad karo jab hum ne is ko aur is ke sab ghar walon ko nijaat di
37,135,siwaye aik budiya ke jo peechay reh jaane walon mein se thi
37,136,phir baqi sab ko tehass nehass kar diya
37,137,aaj tum shab o roz unn ke ujre deyaar par se guzarte ho
37,138,kya tum ko aqal nahi aati ?
37,139,aur yaqeenan Younis bhi Rasolo-n mein se tha
37,140,yaad karo jab woh aik bhari kashti ki taraf bhaag nikla
37,141,phir quraa andazi mein shareek howa aur is mein maat khayi
37,142,aakhir kaar machhli ne usay nigal liya aur woh malamat zada tha
37,143,ab agar woh tasbeeh karne walon mein se nah hota to
37,144,roz qayamat taq isi machhli ke pait mein rehta
37,145,aakhir kaar hum ne usay barri saqeem haalat mein aik chtyal zameen par pheink diya
37,146,aur uss par aik bail daar darakht uga diya
37,147,"is ke baad hum ne ussay aik laakh, ya is se zayed logon ki taraf bheja"
37,148,woh imaan laaye aur hum ne aik waqt khaas taq inhen baqi rakha
37,149,"phir zara inn logon se pucho, kya ( inn ke dil ko yeh baat lagti hai ke ) tumahray rab ke liye to hon betiyan aur un ke liye hon betay !"
37,150,kya waqai hum ne mulaika ko aurtain hi bana ya hai aur yeh aankhon dekhi baat keh rahay hain ?
37,151,"khoob sun rakho, darasal yeh log apni mann gharat se yeh baat kehte hain"
37,152,"ke Allah aulaad rakhta hai, aur fi al waqea yeh jhutay hain"
37,153,kya Allah ne beiton ke bajaye betiyan apne liye pasand kar len ?
